eaking Wigglewalker\"<hr>\"London Frog\n| WrittenBy = Peter Hannan<hr>Mark Haslett\n| Aux2 = Dan Becker & Eric David Haddad<hr>Tom Smith & Jackie Bae\n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2018|11|21}}<hr>{{Start date|2018|12|11}}\n| Aux3 = [[London]], [[United Kingdom]]\n| ShortSummary = Andy is confused during a trip to a [[London]] supermarket due to the differences between [[British English]] and [[American English]].<hr>Luna helps the kids navigate the London fog to find [[Big Ben]].\n| LineColor = 3198FF\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber = 10\n| Title = Queen for a Day\"<hr>\"Jolly Special Friend\n| WrittenBy = Rachel Lipman<hr>Joe Murray\n| Aux2 = Dan Becker & Eric David Haddad<hr>Tom Smith & Jackie Bae\n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2018|12|13}}\n| Aux3 = [[London]], [[United Kingdom]]\n| ShortSummary = Carmen pretends to be the Queen of [[Buckingham Palace]], but later finds it less fun than she imagined.<hr>Papa Chockers is too sick to make lunch for Se\u00f1or Fabuloso's friend so Leo and his friends go out to get some [[multiculturalism|traditional]] London food for them.\n| LineColor = 3198FF\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber = 11\n| Title = Guitar to Sitar\"<hr>\"Spring Has Not Sprung\n| WrittenBy = Mark Haslett<hr>Peter Hannan\n| Aux2 = Dan Becker & Eric David Haddad<hr>Jackie Bae & Tom Smith\n| Aux3 = [[Delhi]], [[India]]\n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2019|03|04}}\n| ShortSummary = The strings on Carmen's guitar snap while she is writing a song for her mother's birthday and she needs to buy more from the bazaar.<hr>Andy wants to photograph the Springtime colors of Dehli but then an overcast weather turns everything gray.\n| LineColor = 3198FF\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber = 12\n| Title = Where's Luna?\"<hr>\"Pulling Strings\n| WrittenBy = Joe Murray<hr>Rachel Lipman\n| Aux2 =Jackie Bae & Dan Becker<hr>Eric David Haddad & Tom Smith\n| Aux3 = [[Delhi]], [[India]]\n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2019|03|05}}\n| ShortSummary = Luna appea