istory/marching-band.html}}\n\n{{Washington Redskins}}\n\n[[Category:Washington Redskins]]\n[[Category:Musical groups established in 1937]]\n[[Category:1937 establishments in Washington, D.C.]]\n[[Category:NFL marching bands]]\n", "name_user": "Charlesaaronthompson", "label": "safe", "comment": "I updated the URL link to the band's official website in the external links section.", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Washington_Redskins_Marching_Band"}
